{"tid":509703,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曝盧卡古不服摩連奴！無視摩帥指揮後4場3球 E-mail 此主題給朋友","createTime":"2017-12-25T15:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T15:57:13.000Z","uid":30788,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"97e593af8f5b16bf6323ff6e781c79a73ea3c6d5","tid":509703,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:15:51.000Z","msg":"最近一段時間里，曼聯的戰績出現了不小的滑落。但更讓曼聯上下揪心的是，摩連奴和盧卡古之間的關係，似乎也出現了問題。<br />\n　　《太陽報》透露，在本月初的比賽中，摩連奴明確告訴盧卡古，他的位置回撤太后，不夠靠前。當時摩帥在技術區大聲吼盧卡古，但後者根本沒有回應摩帥。摩連奴認為，盧卡古回撤這麼深，這會讓曼聯無法得到威脅對手大門的機會。<br />\n　　在摩帥看來，盧卡古應該頂在球隊最前端，和對手最後一名後衛進行身體對抗，充當球隊柱蠆式。不過，對於摩連奴的看法，盧卡古並不服氣，他堅持自己的立場回撤幫助球隊創造機會。<br />\n　　在盧卡古和摩帥發生爭執後，他的狀態立馬開始回暖。在爭執後的4場曼聯比賽中，盧卡古攻入了3球。《太陽報》認為，盧卡古在最近入球後拒絕慶祝，這與他和摩帥發生爭執有一定關係。<br />\n　　今季，盧卡古狀態起伏不定，他在前10場曼聯比賽中，攻入了多達11球。但在隨後的12場比賽中，他卻只攻入了1球。好在最近盧卡古狀態稍稍有所回暖，但尚未達到球迷和教練的期望值。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/8282630/6/20171225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F8282630%2F6%2F20171225&d=lRlg2Z7IIFWR5If%2B7UwjVjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=92ebfc11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/8282630/6/20171225</a><br />\n<br />\n睇嚟又要捉鬼啦<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/titter.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Ftitter.gif&h=e942c2db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_30.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_30.gif&h=0e76de23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05c0520f715ff57fcda657aadf9cbddc18e36c80","tid":509703,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"兩個助攻睇黎都係為左抗議摩佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40489d5c1db2810824362366e962dc91ba5b0090","tid":509703,"uid":7090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"又逼害我曼"},{"pid":"df8fa1358b0b5bc8bf298865e2b150ededd985c7","tid":509703,"uid":29076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"Email此主題給朋友"},{"pid":"e1ec36953c6065696b30ebdb48cb99a0c6b8a2b0","tid":509703,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}